107
00:06:56,509 --> 00:07:00,209
For being self-taught,
I'm pretty good, aren't I?

108
00:07:00,242 --> 00:07:01,742
IRUKA: I don't understand.

109
00:07:01,776 --> 00:07:03,076
-Hm?

110
00:07:03,109 --> 00:07:04,742
-You have this
astounding ability

111
