to use such high level ninjutsu,
and yet you just waste it.

112
00:07:14,509 --> 00:07:16,509
-There you go, lecturing me.

113
00:07:16,542 --> 00:07:18,242
As always.

114
00:07:18,276 --> 00:07:19,309
So weak.

115
00:07:19,342 --> 00:07:20,576
So naive.

116
00:07:20,609 --> 00:07:21,642
Ha!

117
00:07:21,676 --> 00:07:24,142
Don't start preaching
your morals to me.

118
00:07:24,176 --> 00:07:25,476
You fool!

119
00:07:25,509 --> 00:07:28,742
I have 0 respect for
the likes of you!

120
00:07:28,776 --> 00:07:31,109
In the Leaf village,
I hardened my heart

121
00:07:31,142 --> 00:07:32,876
to carry out my missions.

122
00:07:32,909 --> 00:07:36,342
But did it matter to
you and the others?

123
00:07:36,376 --> 00:07:38,942
No matter how powerful
I became, no matter

124
00:07:38,976 --> 00:07:42,276
how many enemies I took
down, didn't matter!

125
00:07:42,309 --> 00:07:44,742
You people gave me
no respect at all.

126
00:07:44,776 --> 00:07:47,009
Even when I was part of
a team, of my comrades

127
00:07:47,042 --> 00:07:48,842
were all bound by
rules of morality.

128
00:07:51,809 --> 00:07:53,642
-They're trying to get
the secret manuscript.

129
00:07:53,676 --> 00:07:55,809
Back up Mizuki!

130
00:07:55,842 --> 00:07:56,309
-Right.

131
00:08:01,642 --> 00:08:02,576
-Hey.

132
00:08:02,609 --> 00:08:03,576
Are you alright?

133
00:08:03,609 --> 00:08:08,009
-I think so, but I
can't feel my leg.

134
00:08:12,076 --> 00:08:13,142
-What do you think, Mizuki?

135
00:08:16,576 --> 00:08:17,642
-It's no good.

136
00:08:17,676 --> 00:08:18,842
He can't go on.

137
00:08:18,876 --> 00:08:20,009
He's done.

138
00:08:20,042 --> 00:08:22,476
-I see.

139
00:08:22,509 --> 00:08:23,142
All right, then.

140
00:08:23,176 --> 00:08:24,842
Let's withdraw.

141
00:08:24,876 --> 00:08:25,742
Hurry!

142
00:08:25,776 --> 00:08:26,709
-I'm coming.

143
00:08:32,242 --> 00:08:35,809
It's unfortunate, but those who
are no use on the battlefield

144
00:08:35,842 --> 00:08:38,509
only become dead
weight for the rest.

145
00:08:38,542 --> 00:08:41,109
It may just be a minor
injury, but if you

146
00:08:41,142 --> 00:08:43,409
aren't able to get up
and fight, you only

147
00:08:43,442 --> 00:08:44,876
have yourself to blame.

148
00:08:48,409 --> 00:08:53,076
I simply carried out
my mission to the end.

149
00:08:53,109 --> 00:08:57,276
And despite that, you people
in the village, not one of you

150
00:08:57,309 --> 00:08:59,509
showed me the
respect I deserved.

151
