229
00:13:02,819 --> 00:13:04,186
-Talk to me.

230
00:13:04,219 --> 00:13:07,119
What's the matter, big bro?

231
00:13:07,153 --> 00:13:08,719
All right!

232
00:13:08,753 --> 00:13:12,253
