do to my big brother?

235
00:13:20,519 --> 00:13:25,386
-I hijacked his body, moron!

236
00:13:25,419 --> 00:13:27,819
Whoa, what the heck?

237
00:13:27,853 --> 00:13:28,786
-Huh?

238
00:13:28,819 --> 00:13:30,319
-Big brother!

239
00:13:30,353 --> 00:13:31,686
Wake up!

240
00:13:31,719 --> 00:13:33,486
Snap out of it already!

241
00:13:37,586 --> 00:13:38,253
-No.

242
00:13:38,286 --> 00:13:39,019
He's just too strong.

243
00:13:42,353 --> 00:13:43,819
Ino, are you OK?

244
00:13:43,853 --> 00:13:45,786
-Well, I think so.

245
00:13:45,819 --> 00:13:48,986
