246
00:13:49,019 --> 00:13:50,419
My gorgeous face!

247
00:13:50,453 --> 00:13:53,319
No!

248
00:13:53,353 --> 00:13:54,553
-Women.

249
00:13:54,586 --> 00:13:55,586
Give me a break.

250
00:13:55,619 --> 00:13:57,019
[screaming]

251
00:13:57,053 --> 00:13:57,786
-No.

252
00:13:57,819 --> 00:14:00,286
Choji.

253
00:14:00,319 --> 00:14:01,619
Choji!

254
00:14:01,653 --> 00:14:02,919
-Aw, man.

255
00:14:02,953 --> 00:14:04,086
-Are you OK, pal?

256
00:14:04,119 --> 00:14:06,553
-Well, I'm not dead.

257
00:14:06,586 --> 00:14:07,519
-Sorry.

258
00:14:07,553 --> 00:14:09,486
Feels like I fell asleep.

259
00:14:09,519 --> 00:14:10,019
-Hey.

260
00:14:10,053 --> 00:14:10,953
Big brother.

261
00:14:10,986 --> 00:14:13,053
You're all better now.

262
00:14:13,086 --> 00:14:15,119
SHIKAMARU (VOICEOVER):
Aw, what a drag.

263
00:14:15,153 --> 00:14:16,986
I guess I gotta use this.

264
00:14:17,019 --> 00:14:18,086
K, here we go.

265
00:14:18,119 --> 00:14:19,386
Shadow Strangle Jutsu.

266
00:14:25,153 --> 00:14:27,853
-Big brother.

267
00:14:27,886 --> 00:14:29,153
-How dare you?

268
00:14:34,853 --> 00:14:36,886
-We're getting closer
now, and Mizuki

269
00:14:36,919 --> 00:14:38,086
may have set a trap for us.

270
00:14:38,119 --> 00:14:39,686
Be careful with every step.

271
00:14:39,719 --> 00:14:41,319
-Yeah, I kind of
figured he would.

272
00:14:50,753 --> 00:14:55,886
MIZUKI: It was so enjoyable,
