00:14:57,719 --> 00:14:59,153
The unrelenting gloom.

275
00:15:04,686 --> 00:15:06,153
Pitch black all year round.

276
00:15:09,886 --> 00:15:12,219
That darkness made me stronger.

277
00:15:12,253 --> 00:15:15,386
It's how I mastered techniques
an ordinary shinobi would never

278
00:15:15,419 --> 00:15:16,453
have learned.

279
00:15:16,486 --> 00:15:18,553
Even in these
shadows, I am still

280
00:15:18,586 --> 00:15:20,219
able to sense your energy.

281
00:15:26,519 --> 00:15:27,353
What's the matter?

282
00:15:27,386 --> 00:15:28,853
Tuckered out already?

283
00:15:33,286 --> 00:15:36,053
Now's not the time to lose
your concentration, Iruka.

284
00:15:36,086 --> 00:15:37,153
This is fun.

285
00:15:37,186 --> 00:15:38,519
I wanna make it last.

286
00:15:38,553 --> 00:15:40,086
Let's take our time.

287
00:15:51,119 --> 00:15:51,853
-All right.

288
00:15:51,886 --> 00:15:52,753
My turn.

289
00:15:52,786 --> 00:15:53,819
-Ino, wait.

290
00:15:53,853 --> 00:15:55,686
If you use your mind
transfer technique,

291
00:15:55,719 --> 00:15:58,419
my Strangle Jutsu is
just gonna hurt you, too.

292
00:15:58,453 --> 00:15:59,486
-Hmph.

293
00:15:59,519 --> 00:16:00,886
If you think are you're
the only one who's

294
00:16:00,919 --> 00:16:04,819
learned a cool new technique,
Shikamaru, you can kiss my ass.

295
00:16:04,853 --> 00:16:05,819
-Huh?

296
00:16:05,853 --> 00:16:08,086
-Ninja Art, Mind
Destruction Jutsu!

297
00:16:14,186 --> 00:16:16,186
-Hey, wha-- What is it?

298
00:16:16,219 --> 00:16:16,719
Hey, Raijin!

299
00:16:22,119 --> 00:16:22,719
Raijin!

300
00:16:22,753 --> 00:16:24,786
What are you doing?

301
00:16:24,819 --> 00:16:25,753
-Nice.

302
00:16:25,786 --> 00:16:28,186
Not a bad move there.

303
00:16:28,219 --> 00:16:29,519
-So glad you like it.

304
00:16:29,553 --> 00:16:30,553
The new Ino collection.

305
00:16:39,786 --> 00:16:42,853
-Almost there.

306
00:16:42,886 --> 00:16:44,686
Ah.

307
00:16:44,719 --> 00:16:45,453
That's it.

308
00:16:45,486 --> 00:16:46,519
That building!

309
00:16:46,553 --> 00:16:47,853
-All right.

310
00:16:47,886 --> 00:16:49,619
Just a few mot steps
and we're there!

311
00:17:05,686 --> 00:17:07,019
MIZUKI: Well, Iruka?

312
00:17:07,053 --> 00:17:09,453
Have your eyes adjusted at all?

313
00:17:09,486 --> 00:17:12,753
For guys like you who live
their lives in the light,

314
00:17:12,786 --> 00:17:14,586
darkness can be a
bit of a problem.

315
00:17:21,453 --> 00:17:22,386
-Come on.

316
00:17:22,419 --> 00:17:23,353
Where is he?

317
00:17:31,686 --> 00:17:33,619
-Hey, Iruka.

318
00:17:33,653 --> 00:17:35,153
What were you saying
before about how

319
00:17:35,186 --> 00:17:37,719
you were going to
bring this to an end?

320
00:17:37,753 --> 00:17:38,486
Oh.

321
00:17:38,519 --> 00:17:40,053
I see.

322
00:17:40,086 --> 00:17:44,486
By bring this to an end, you
were talking about yourself.

323
00:17:44,519 --> 00:17:47,353
[evil laughter]

324
00:17:51,886 --> 00:17:52,653
-Almost.

325
00:17:52,686 --> 00:17:54,253
Give them a little bit more.

326
00:17:54,286 --> 00:17:54,819
-Yeah, Ino.

327
00:17:54,853 --> 00:17:55,486
Hang in there.

328
00:17:55,519 --> 00:17:56,586
-We got these guys.

329
00:18:05,419 --> 00:18:06,586
-No way.

330
00:18:06,619 --> 00:18:08,219
These idiots are so strong.

331
00:18:08,253 --> 00:18:09,186
-Those jerks.

332
00:18:09,219 --> 00:18:10,686
They don't stop.

333
00:18:15,853 --> 00:18:18,453
I don't think I can
hold them back anymore.

334
00:18:18,486 --> 00:18:20,853
SHIKAMARU (VOICEOVER): If we
release this jutsu right now,

335
00:18:20,886 --> 00:18:23,286
all our work will
be for nothing.

336
00:18:23,319 --> 00:18:24,053
Come on.

337
00:18:24,086 --> 00:18:25,186
Think about the next move.

338
00:18:27,919 --> 00:18:29,486
[grunting]

339
00:18:29,519 --> 00:18:31,586
-Hang in there.

340
00:18:31,619 --> 00:18:32,319
-Ino.

341
00:18:32,353 --> 00:18:33,719
I've gotta do something.

342
00:18:33,753 --> 00:18:34,553
-Why?

343
00:18:34,586 --> 00:18:35,953
So they can knock you out again?

344
00:18:35,986 --> 00:18:36,753
-Ino.

345
00:18:36,786 --> 00:18:38,486
Just shut up and watch.

346
00:18:38,519 --> 00:18:43,119
Even the chubby guy's got
some skills when he tries.

347
00:18:43,153 --> 00:18:46,819
[scream]

348
00:18:46,853 --> 00:18:49,919
-Here's my Partial
Expansion Jutsu!

349
00:18:49,953 --> 00:18:50,519
Both hands!

350
00:18:54,319 --> 00:18:59,186
[screaming]

351
00:18:59,219 --> 00:19:00,653
-Choji.

352
00:19:00,686 --> 00:19:03,619
-Well, I couldn't just sit back
and let you have all the fun,

353
00:19:03,653 --> 00:19:05,753
could I, Ino?

354
00:19:05,786 --> 00:19:06,953
That's right, suckers.

355
00:19:06,986 --> 00:19:09,253
You're looking at the
number one handsome chubby

356
00:19:09,286 --> 00:19:10,453
ninja in the land.

357
00:19:10,486 --> 00:19:12,719
-You're amazing, Choji!

358
00:19:12,753 --> 00:19:15,086
So cool!

359
00:19:15,119 --> 00:19:16,253
-That's my Choji.

360
00:19:16,286 --> 00:19:19,853
Brand new formation,
Ino Shika Cho complete.

361
00:19:26,819 --> 00:19:28,519
-That's strange.

362
00:19:28,553 --> 00:19:31,919
Mizuki-- I don't
sense his presence.

363
00:19:31,953 --> 00:19:33,119
It's too quiet.

364
00:19:44,219 --> 00:19:45,186
That's not it.

365
00:19:53,119 --> 00:19:55,086
It's even deeper.

366
00:19:55,119 --> 00:19:59,053
[heartbeat]

367
00:20:34,286 --> 00:20:36,053
-Are those footsteps?

368
00:20:36,086 --> 00:20:36,953
No.

369
00:20:36,986 --> 00:20:39,186
They're not.

370
00:20:39,219 --> 00:20:41,786
It sounds different
from footsteps.

371
00:20:41,819 --> 00:20:43,219
Subtler.

372
00:20:43,253 --> 00:20:44,886
Smaller.

373
00:20:44,919 --> 00:20:47,086
More steady.

374
00:20:47,119 --> 00:20:51,419
The sound-- of a paper bomb!

375
00:21:01,253 --> 00:21:02,586
-Was that some kind of bomb?

376
00:21:13,586 --> 00:21:14,819
-What happened in there?

377
00:21:17,619 --> 00:21:19,219
-Iruka-sensei!

378
00:21:19,253 --> 00:21:21,552
Iruka-sensei!

379
00:21:30,558 --> 00:21:34,925
[theme music]

380
00:23:02,458 --> 00:23:04,258
-I can't believe this.

381
00:23:04,292 --> 00:23:05,125
What just happened?

382
00:23:05,158 --> 00:23:06,892
Where's Iruka-sensei?

383
00:23:06,925 --> 00:23:08,658
-His scent ends here.

384
00:23:08,692 --> 00:23:11,392
The only thing we can do
now is search the vicinity.

385
00:23:11,425 --> 00:23:13,625
-This whole place is destroyed.

386
00:23:13,658 --> 00:23:14,625
No!

387
00:23:14,658 --> 00:23:16,425
Iruka-sensei, I hope
you're still alive!

388
00:23:16,458 --> 00:23:17,258
PAKKUN: Shh!

389
00:23:17,292 --> 00:23:19,358
Keep your voice down, Naruto!

390
00:23:19,392 --> 00:23:23,092
I think someone may
be coming this way.

391
00:23:23,125 --> 00:23:25,192
NARUTO: Next time,
Orochimaru's Shadow!

392
00:23:30,325 --> 00:23:33,825
[theme music]

